{"tid":1428634,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［612人道基金籌款post］想麻煩大學巴絲填個講exchange的問卷","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T06:03:23.000Z","uid":284565,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6abdf871990bca2e28df78749d05b56443b76897","tid":1428634,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"係呢種時候，身為P 牌仔咁同大家講都唔係太好意思......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹最近有份工係大學做問卷調查，需要270 位UGC funded 嘅undergrad（<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>有去過exchange 的話更加需要</strong></span>，有個sample size，唔可以太多太少）填份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n每填一份問卷，我人工會多25蚊，呢筆錢全部會用作612 人道支緩基金捐款。link 係下面，希望大家幫幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n個 project 越快完，我越快可以confirm 到人工。我到時捐左錢會放入數紙上黎（270*25 = 6750）。數字雖小，但大家用5分鐘填份問卷就可以幫到小小，唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則話理論上可以亂填，不過呢份問卷調查嘅結果對大學生未來exchange 都可能有多少影響，所以設左問題要大家嘅學生電郵（絕對唔會send 野俾你）。請各位巴絲唔好亂填，或者填幾份，data 會作廢。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b618d953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6</a><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"aeac82e38b2bd9f5b71916631de72e4c789f64a3","tid":1428634,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e960a845fbe0ea44d8981dcbe41a22723ea04a81","tid":1428634,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a536557dddb05fdd5ac5ef6d4b8778bbc5586f8e","tid":1428634,"uid":284565,"